name: A Journey Through Greece
description:
This is what I saw while I was high on shrooms in Greece ;)


This picture was taken in Athens, Greece.
I use an A7R3 for my camera.
Image is ~42 MP and was edited as a RAW in photoshop + after effects.

All photography🖼️ was produced and edited by 🔥Dennis Sarovski🔥
